@HealthCheckDemo_HostAddress = http://localhost:5289

### Summary probe — plain-text status (200 Healthy/Degraded, 503 Unhealthy)
GET {{HealthCheckDemo_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: text/plain

###

### Liveness probe — system checks only (memory, disk), JSON
GET {{HealthCheckDemo_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Readiness probe — startup gate + external dependency, JSON
GET {{HealthCheckDemo_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### Full detail — all checks, rich JSON report
GET {{HealthCheckDemo_HostAddress}}/health/detail
Accept: application/json

###
